{"medsNode":"sunken_25","medsPercent":100,"medsPriority":0,"Description":"You arrive at the chamber where the enslaved cold-blooded race people live. This must be the place the naga told you about. The room is crowded, but you don’t see any guards nearby. It looks like the guards let the prisoners organize themselves in this slum.

It would be easy for you to interact with the slaves and even try to free them. To your surprise, they have all the tools for breaking their chains within reach. Probably the fear of retaliation is the only thing that keeps them from revolting.
